# AJDO.apk har push'da GitHub Actions tomonidan avtomatik qayta yig'iladi
# (deploy.yml#build-apk) va qayta commit qilinadi — hajmi 100+ MB'gacha
# yetishi mumkin, GitHub'ning ODDIY git obyekti uchun 100 MB qattiq
# chegarasidan oshib ketishi mumkin ("File ... exceeds GitHub's file size
# limit" xatosi shu sababdan). Git LFS orqali saqlash bu chegarani olib
# tashlaydi (LFS fayllari alohida, katta hajmli saqlash uchun mo'ljallangan).
#
# MUHIM: bu fayllar public/ ICHIDA EMAS (downloads/, ILDIZ darajasida) —
# aks holda `vite build`/`npx cap sync android` ularni HAR safar dist/
# orqali Android/Electron ilovaning O'ZINING ICHIGA (assets) nusxalab
# qo'yardi — 200+ MB keraksiz binary Gradle'ning compressDebugAssets
# bosqichida "Java heap space" (xotira tugashi) xatosiga sabab bo'lgan
# edi. downloads/ Dockerfile'da ALOHIDA (dist/'dan mustaqil) nginx
# image'iga COPY qilinadi.
downloads/*.apk filter=lfs diff=lfs merge=lfs -text
# AJDO-Setup.exe (Electron — Chromium+Node bundlangani uchun odatda
# APK'dan HAM kattaroq, 150+ MB) — xuddi shu sabab bilan LFS orqali.
downloads/desktop/*.exe filter=lfs diff=lfs merge=lfs -text
downloads/desktop/*.blockmap filter=lfs diff=lfs merge=lfs -text
